window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The town of Vismuth has enemies closing in from both sides. Hordes of beastmen come from the Deadlands in the north. The Draconic Empire marches from the south.</b></p> <p>John Devonte now calls Vismuth home, and he’s not willing to let it go so easily. He’s armed with his beautiful Wargear women, and the blood of the True Dragon flows through his veins.</p> <p>But will his newfound power be enough? Or will John and his women find their beloved town ravished—or worse, will the bond between them be torn asunder?</p>"; 
